00:31:35.960 --> 00:31:38.240
long-suffering, charity, patience,

00:31:38.240 --> 00:31:40.040
persecutions, afflictions,

00:31:40.040 --> 00:31:42.280
which came unto Me at Antioch,

00:31:42.280 --> 00:31:43.720
at Iconium, at Lystra,

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:45.640
what persecutions I endured,

00:31:45.640 --> 00:31:49.200
