00:33:18.760 --> 00:33:20.400
And then he tells Timothy,

00:33:20.480 --> 00:33:25.360
but evil men and seducers shall wax worse and worse,

00:33:25.360 --> 00:33:28.720
deceiving and being deceived.

00:33:28.720 --> 00:33:32.960
Far too often, as I would go to various conferences

