00:34:06.040 --> 00:34:10.280
No, no, Paul told Timothy, but continue.

00:34:11.880 --> 00:34:13.800
You mean to tell me that in the midst

00:34:13.800 --> 00:34:15.840
of what you've just described

00:34:15.840 --> 00:34:18.960
and all of these characteristics that are mentioned

00:34:18.960 --> 00:34:21.080
with the truth that evil men and seducers

00:34:21.080 --> 00:34:22.400
