00:34:54.840 --> 00:34:57.520
that I didn't get saved while I was a child.

00:34:58.920 --> 00:35:01.840
I was almost an adult when I got saved.

00:35:01.840 --> 00:35:03.120
I know that Joyce often,

00:35:03.120 --> 00:35:04.840
when she shares her testimony of salvation,

00:35:04.840 --> 00:35:07.560
you were in your 30s when you trusted Christ as your Savior.

00:35:07.560 --> 00:35:10.120
Some say, man, I was even older than that.

00:35:10.120 --> 00:35:13.240
But here, Paul says to Timothy that from a child,

00:35:13.240 --> 00:35:14.760
thou hast known the Holy Scriptures,

00:35:14.760 --> 00:35:16.920
which are able to make thee wise unto salvation.

00:35:16.920 --> 00:35:18.520
And what a joy that is.

00:35:18.520 --> 00:35:21.240
He says all Scripture is given by inspiration of God.

00:35:21.240 --> 00:35:22.120
It's profitable.

00:35:22.120 --> 00:35:23.400
Well, look what he says.

00:35:23.400 --> 00:35:24.680
It's profitable for what?

00:35:24.680 --> 00:35:26.560
For doctrine, for reproof, for correction,

00:35:26.560 --> 00:35:28.160
for instruction in righteousness.

00:35:28.160 --> 00:35:29.440
We read verse number 17

00:35:29.440 --> 00:35:31.200
in the beginning of the message this evening

00:35:31.200 --> 00:35:34.000
when it said that Noah was perfect in his generations.

00:35:34.000 --> 00:35:35.720
And we noticed here, the Bible says

00:35:35.720 --> 00:35:37.120
that the man of God may be perfect,

00:35:37.120 --> 00:35:39.120
thoroughly furnished unto all good works.

00:35:39.120 --> 00:35:41.920
But notice how Paul continues into chapter number four.

00:35:41.920 --> 00:35:43.680
He issues a charge.

00:35:43.680 --> 00:35:45.480
He says, I charge thee.

00:35:45.480 --> 00:35:49.160
Therefore, before God and the Lord Jesus Christ,

00:35:49.160 --> 00:35:51.120
who shall judge the quick and the dead

00:35:51.120 --> 00:35:52.240
that is appearing in this kingdom.

00:35:52.240 --> 00:35:53.480
What's he telling them to do?

00:35:53.480 --> 00:35:54.520
Preach the word.

00:35:55.920 --> 00:35:57.360
Hold on a minute.

00:35:57.360 --> 00:35:59.140
Chapter three is still there.

00:35:59.140 --> 00:36:01.000
All of those characteristics.

00:36:01.000 --> 00:36:02.880
Evil men waxing worse and worse,

00:36:02.880 --> 00:36:04.600
deceiving and being deceived.

00:36:04.600 --> 00:36:08.320
And yet, Paul tells Timothy, preach the word.

00:36:10.120 --> 00:36:11.600
Preach the word.

00:36:11.600 --> 00:36:14.440
He tells them here, be instant insees and outsees

00:36:14.440 --> 00:36:16.080
and reprove, rebuke, and exhort

00:36:16.080 --> 00:36:17.720
with all longsuffering and doctrine.

00:36:17.720 --> 00:36:19.160
Notice verses three and four.

00:36:19.160 --> 00:36:21.120
It says, for the time will come

00:36:21.120 --> 00:36:24.480
when they will not endure sound doctrine.

00:36:24.480 --> 00:36:25.720
