00:36:33.480 --> 00:36:36.260
and shall be turned unto fables.

00:36:36.260 --> 00:36:38.320
But watch down all things, endure afflictions,

00:36:38.320 --> 00:36:39.400
do the work of evangelists,

00:36:39.400 --> 00:36:42.240
make full proof of thy ministry.

00:36:43.080 --> 00:36:48.080
Paul to Timothy, he says, listen.

00:36:50.560 --> 00:36:52.880
Here's the characteristics of the last days.

00:36:53.760 --> 00:36:55.240
Here's what's going to happen.

00:36:56.360 --> 00:36:58.960
But Timothy, the message is continue.

00:36:58.960 --> 00:37:00.840
And for us this evening,

00:37:00.840 --> 00:37:04.100
the call for us as God's people today

00:37:04.100 --> 00:37:07.440
