00:37:09.800 --> 00:37:12.160
We just keep our eyes on Jesus

00:37:12.960 --> 00:37:14.080
and we just keep on preaching the word of God

00:37:14.080 --> 00:37:16.200
and doing what God called us to do,

00:37:16.200 --> 00:37:20.440
living as lights in a crooked and perverse generation.

00:37:20.440 --> 00:37:23.760
That we would, listen, we might face ridicule,

00:37:23.760 --> 00:37:25.080
but the Bible says all those

00:37:25.080 --> 00:37:26.400
that live godly in Christ Jesus

00:37:26.400 --> 00:37:28.360
