00:37:39.960 --> 00:37:41.880
and it pales in comparison

00:37:41.880 --> 00:37:43.680
to what some of our brothers and sisters

00:37:43.680 --> 00:37:46.080
in other parts of this world face today.

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:51.400
We find that the answer is that we,

00:37:51.400 --> 00:37:53.680
as God's people, would continue.

00:37:53.680 --> 00:37:57.240
See, Noah, he lived in the midst of that society

00:37:57.240 --> 00:38:00.060
