00:38:00.060 --> 00:38:01.400
because of the wickedness

00:38:01.400 --> 00:38:03.640
and God defines all of that to us,

00:38:03.640 --> 00:38:06.700
but we find that Noah continued to walk with God.

00:38:07.620 --> 00:38:11.540
And this evening, who's walking with God?

00:38:12.540 --> 00:38:13.740
Are we walking with God?

00:38:14.620 --> 00:38:18.100
