of this state and say, here's the characteristics,

00:38:32.540 --> 00:38:34.020
here's what's going on,

00:38:34.020 --> 00:38:36.740
but I got some people that are walking with me.

00:38:36.740 --> 00:38:40.260
I got some people that are living and shining

00:38:40.260 --> 00:38:43.380
and they're doing what they're supposed to do

00:38:43.380 --> 00:38:46.340
because God's issued this call to us.

00:38:46.340 --> 00:38:49.540
And it's not appropriate that we would make excuses

00:38:49.540 --> 00:38:52.780
and that we would allow the society to influence us.

00:38:52.780 --> 00:38:55.940
One of the major problems in the church in Corinth

00:38:55.940 --> 00:38:58.420
