00:39:36.340 --> 00:39:38.500
And we stand upon the truth of the word of God.

00:39:38.500 --> 00:39:43.180
Listen, our nation needs revival.

00:39:43.180 --> 00:39:45.420
They need to see that God is real.

00:39:47.060 --> 00:39:48.760
